; Test commodity comparison with fixated vs non-fixated prices
; Covers commodity.cc lines 504-510 (semantic flags comparison in
; compare_by_commodity)

2024/01/01 Buy regular
    Assets:Brokerage    10 AAPL {$150.00}
    Assets:Cash        $-1500.00

2024/01/02 Buy fixated
    Assets:Brokerage    5 AAPL {=$150.00}
    Assets:Cash         $-750.00

test bal --no-total --lots Brokerage
   10 AAPL {$150.00}
   5 AAPL {=$150.00}  Assets:Brokerage
end test
